        title: "Notes on Old English grammar (Notebook 29, Bodleian Library)",
        printedIn: "Simon Horobin, “Translations from <i>Beowulf</i> by C.S. Lewis,” <i>The Journal of Inklings Studies</i>",
        issueOrVolume: "vol. 14, no. 2",
