        printedIn: "George Sayer, “Recollections of J.R.R. Tolkien,” <i>Proceedings of the J.R.R. Tolkien Centenary Conference 1992,</i> eds. Patricia Reynolds and Glen GoodKnight, <i>Mythlore</i>",
        issueOrVolume: "vol. 21, no. 2",
        pageRange: "21",
