        year: 1952,
        monthAndDay: "28 February",
        textProvided: "Thank you for sending me your article, which is at once terrifying and consoling, and always of absorbing interest. Alas! I do not find any of it “inconceivable”. I wish it were more widely known to the fools in the free countries who still rally with Bolshevism.<br><br>With all good wishes to yourself, yours sincerely,<br><br>C.S. Lewis.",
        type: "Letter",
