        year: 2023,
        monthAndDay: null,
        textProvided: "Magdalene College, Cambridge<br>17/1/58<br><br>Dear Shepherd<br><br>Oh I’ll read the Introduction alright: I’d thought it was a question of going through the text and notes word by word!<br><br>Yours<br>C.S. Lewis",
