        textProvided: "Hedgehog hase ane sturne rynde<br>uppon his bak wha sall it se<br>bot wambe and brest after his kynde<br>bathe is softe as silk harde.<br>þat ane signifyeþ to my mynde<br>fortitude al witerle<br>þat oper as man iwriten finde<br>þe noble vertue of charitee<br>Whan þat he is idrad of fas<br>intill ane bal then torneþ he<br>what mister beste ojeins him gas<br>can nat gar him grue ne dee<br>his heued he ligges untill his tas<br>þat lowest to þat heizest sal bee<br>quhilk signifyeþ as in this cas<br>guid skeltrom is in humilitee.<br>EXPLICIT.",
