        textProvided: "On Monday morning<br>I work till one! Hoike!!<br>Piddling pupils<br>I in taking am engaged!!<br>Can your car<br>So swiftly over<br>Earth’s back wander<br>From Oxford to London between one and 5:45?<br>Walawei? Hoo-ruddy-rah!!!!<br>Ho-hei!!!!!<br>!!<br>?!!!! . . . . .<br>If so, to call<br>For me at Magdalen<br>Were wisest rune<br>On Monday at one!<br>If you lie<br>On Teusday [sic] night<br>In Magdalen’s ancient College<br>You will meet Dyson<br>Dining with me<br>Of men the justest!!<br>(The whole scene explodes)",
